r mark muted \">......</div>\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"消音標記的注意事項"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"消音標記的注意事項"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"關於消音標記比較需要注意的是，如果你點擊展開的那則噗是被消音的，那麼回覆區的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<div class=\"plurk_box\">......</div>"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 也會有 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"muted"}]},{"type":"text","value":" class。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"<!-- 示例：點擊被消音的噗文時的連貫作用\n<div id=\"timeline_holder\">\n  <div id=\"timeline_cnt\">\n    <div class=\"block_cnt\">\n      <!-- 點擊這則被消音的噗文 -->\n      <div class=\"plurk cboxAncho muted display\">......</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 噗文的回覆區；當點被消音的噗文時，這邊也會加上 muted class -->\n<div id=\"form_holder\" class=\"plurk_box muted\">......</div>\n","language":"html"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<!-- 示例：點擊被消音的噗文時的連貫作用\n<div id=\"timeline_holder\">\n  <div id=\"timeline_cnt\">\n    <div class=\"block_cnt\">\n      <!-- 點擊這則被消音的噗文 -->\n      <div class=\"plurk cboxAncho muted display\">......</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 噗文的回覆區；當點被消音的噗文時，這邊也會加上 muted class -->\n<div id=\"form_holder\" class=\"plurk_box muted\">......</div>\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"實作樣式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"實作樣式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在本章列出幾種情境、需求，並且附上示例給讀者參考。記得每次更改要看效果時，都要重新整理噗浪的網站哦。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"讓被消音的噗文變得不明顯"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓被消音的噗文變得不明顯"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回顧需求，如果想要讓被消音的噗文變得不明顯，最直白的作法就是增加該噗元素的透明度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":".muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但是由於上節說的連貫作用，會導致展開被消音噗文的留言時，留言區也會變成不明顯的。如果本來就沒打算看已消音噗的留言時，倒是不需要再作修改。但如果有要回顧留言的需求，那建議還是將被透明化的元素定義的精準一點："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".plurk.muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":".plurk.muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"讓鼠標移到消音的噗文時弱化透明化的效果"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓鼠標移到消音的噗文時，弱化透明化的效果"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雖然把消音的噗給淡化了，但有時候可能還是會想知道上面寫什麼，比較折衷的方式，就是讓鼠標移上去時，減弱透明化的效果，所以我們再透過 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":":hover"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 修飾目標："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".plurk.muted:hover {\n  opacity: 0.95; \n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":".plurk.muted:hover {\n  opacity: 0.95; \n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"改變噗文背景顏色"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改變噗文背景顏色"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"針對消音的部分做改善後，接下來針對想要將被標籤、被加到最愛的噗文加入比較不一樣的特徵，讓我可以一眼看出該噗就是被標記或是被加最愛。這裏實作的方式是改變噗文的背景顏色，不過修飾的目標不再是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<div class=\"plurk\"></div>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，而是該元素內只有包括內文的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<div class=\"plurk_cnt\"></div>"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 元素，實際差異可以透過瀏覽器的開發者工具查看，這裡就不多贅述。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將被加入書籤的噗文背景色改成"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"瓶覗"}]},{"type":"text","value":"綠："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".plurk.mark .plurk_cnt{\n    background: rgb(225, 254, 223)\n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":".plurk.mark .plurk_cnt{\n    background: rgb(225, 254, 223)\n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將被加到最愛的噗文背景色改成"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桜色"}]},{"type":"text","value":"粉，並考慮如果一篇噗文同時被加入書籤和最愛時，已加入最愛的顏色為主："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".plurk.favorite .plurk_cnt, \n.mark.favorite .plurk_cnt {\n  background: rgb(254, 223, 225)\n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":".plurk.favorite .plurk_cnt, \n.mark.favorite .plurk_cnt {\n  background: rgb(254, 223, 225)\n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"多重標記處理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多重標記處理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如上小節有提到可能會有一篇噗文會有多重標記的情況，也要一一作處理。同是更改背景色為效果的標記，若同時都有時該以哪個標記為主、如果被加最愛的標記也被消音時，是不是讓透明度效果不要那麼強、等等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這邊以減弱被消音的書籤、最愛噗文的透明度效果為例："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":".plurk.muted.mark {\n  opacity: 0.7;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted.favorite {\n  opacity: 0.9;\n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text