background: rgb(213, 251, 255)\n}\n\n/* Favorite */\n.plurk.favorite .plurk_cnt, \n.plurk.mark.favorite .plurk_cnt {\n  background: rgb(254, 223, 225); \n}\n\n/* R18 ; Behind the attention */\n.plurk.porn .td_cnt .text_holder{\n  filter: blur(3px);\n}\n\n.plurk.porn .td_cnt .text_holder:hover{\n  filter: none;\n}\n\n/* Muted */\n.plurk.muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted.mark {\n  opacity: 0.7;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted.favorite {\n  opacity: 0.9;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted:hover {\n  opacity: 0.95; \n}\n","language":"css"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"/* Mark */\n.plurk.mark .plurk_cnt {\n    background: rgb(213, 251, 255)\n}\n\n/* Favorite */\n.plurk.favorite .plurk_cnt, \n.plurk.mark.favorite .plurk_cnt {\n  background: rgb(254, 223, 225); \n}\n\n/* R18 ; Behind the attention */\n.plurk.porn .td_cnt .text_holder{\n  filter: blur(3px);\n}\n\n.plurk.porn .td_cnt .text_holder:hover{\n  filter: none;\n}\n\n/* Muted */\n.plurk.muted {\n  opacity: 0.2;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted.mark {\n  opacity: 0.7;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted.favorite {\n  opacity: 0.9;\n}\n\n.plurk.muted:hover {\n  opacity: 0.95; \n}\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"結語"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"結語"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這篇文章算是自己針對需求進行修改後，順帶產生的一篇教學文。其中更改的元素並不多，只專注在噗文的背景色和透明度上，但其實噗浪自訂 CSS 的功能是還可以做出更多變化的，這部分網路上應該也有文章在講了，有興趣進一步的朋友可以找找看資料。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文章所示範的顏色是以預設的河道樣式為底去套用的，不一定適用於各位的河道上，所以要套用什麼顏色、多少透明度就煩請各位依照自己的河道樣式慢慢測試囉。懂網頁開發的朋友也可以針對文字顏色去做改變，或是進一步做點配套設計。等哪天我有空，或許就會在整理一篇文章專門在講修改哪些類別可以改變河道上什麼元素的樣式吧。嗯，有空的話。 XDD"}]}]},"title_en":"Change style of marked plurk","slug":"change-style-of-marked-plurk","aliases":["更改噗浪被標記噗文的樣式","Change style of marked plurk"],"created_at":"2017-12-12T22:11:19.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":["web"],"